            "title": "台股收跌逾1.8%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">台灣加權指數收報32572點，跌602點，跌幅1.82%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">台股明日假期休市，全星期跌逾1.6%。</p>\n</div>",
